<h3 id="metronome">
<a class="heading-anchor" href="#metronome" hidden><svg width="16" height="16"><use xlink:href="https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#anchor"></use></svg></a>Metronome <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/aplazas/metronome"><svg width='16' height='16'><use xlink:href='https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#link'></use></svg></a>
